{
  "title": "GeoParams.jl: A Julia package for managing material parameters in geodynamic simulations",
  "description": "GeoParams.jl is a Julia package that simplifies the management of material parameters and constitutive relationships for geodynamic simulations. It provides tools for nondimensionalization, parameter specification, and efficient, allocation-free computational routines for both CPUs and GPUs.",
  "notes": "Additional funding: (1) PASC GPU4GEO - Frontier GPU multi-physics solvers (c23), funded by ETH Zurich. Project page: https://www.pasc-ch.org/projects/2021-2024/gpu4geo/ and (2) )",
